Method Detail

addMetricsProgressListener

public void addMetricsProgressListener(IMetricsProgressListener l)
Add listener l to be notified of metrics progress. If there are any calculations already ongoing, l will be caught up by the immediate receipt on the current thread of a queued event with the current number of outstanding calculations.

l -
